<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #e94057;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e94057;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #e94057;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Amora Hub!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for signing up for Amora Hub. Please click the button below to verify your email address and complete your registration.</p>
            <a href="<%= verificationURL %>" class="button">Verify Email</a>
            <p>If you did not create an account, no further action is required.</p>
            <p>Alternatively, you can use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your account:</p>
            <h2 style="text-align: center; font-size: 36px; letter-spacing: 5px; margin: 30px 0;"><%= otp %></h2>
            <p>This OTP is valid for 10 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you're having trouble with the button, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <p><a href="<%= verificationURL %>"><%= verificationURL %></a></p>
            <p>Thank you,<br>The Amora Hub Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Amora Hub. All Rights Reserved.</p>
            <p><a href="https://amorahub.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="https://amorahub.com/terms">Terms of Use</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>